	<h1>About Us</h1>

	<div id="about_header">Unitechange.org was founded to build a new type of philanthropy based on the following observations:</div>

	<div id="about_list">
		<div class="about_number"><img src="/images/circle1.png" alt="1">There is a detachment in current donation services. Everyone should feel a personal connection to the causes they support.</div>

		<div class="about_number"><img src="/images/circle2.png" alt="2">Non-profit organizations often spend too much time trying to raise funds. Instead, great organizations should focus more of their time fulfilling their mission.</div>

		<div class="about_number"><img src="/images/circle3.png" alt="3">Under-served local communities often have little involvement in their own projects. They should be engaged in developing projects.</div>
	</div>
	
