	<div id="about_mission">
		<h1>Our Mission</h1>

		<p>Our goal is to create a more tangible approach to charity, so each donor can feel like a millionaire philanthropist, connected to every step of the project development process. We will broadcast the story of each project as it is being built to you on an ongoing basis through email updates, blogs, photos, and video.</p>

		<p>The goal is to introduce you, our donors, to various community development projects around the world, sponsored by non-profit partner organizations. You can then make small (micro) contributions to one project at a time that you believe in, follow the project as it progresses, and share the story with your friends.</p>

		<p>With support from our non-profit partner organizations, we will work with the local communities to develop the infrastructure they desperately need. Our projects will be identified by members of the local community to determine what they really need, rather than what outsiders think they need.</p>
